{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 36,
  "title": "第三十六章（微明）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "將欲歙之，必固張之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "將欲弱之，必固強之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "將欲廢之，必固興之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "將欲奪之，必固與之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂微明。"
    },
    {
      "text": "柔弱勝剛強。"
    },
    {
      "text": "魚不可脫於淵，"
    },
    {
      "text": "國之利器，不可以示人。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先開張之者，欲極其奢淫。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先強大之者，欲使遇禍患。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先興之者，欲使其驕危。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先與之者，欲極其貪心。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此四事，其道微，其效明也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "柔弱者久長，剛強者先亡也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "魚脫於淵，謂去剛得柔，不可復制焉。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "利器者，謂權道也。治國權者，不可以示執事之臣也。 治身道者，不可以示非其人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
